*bacula-5.0.3 (21 Aug 2010)

  21 Aug 2010; Thomas Beierlein <tomjbe@gentoo.org>
  -files/2.4.4/bacula-default-configs.patch, -files/2.4.4/bacula-dir-conf,
  -files/2.4.4/bacula-dir-init, -files/2.4.4/bacula-fd-conf,
  -files/2.4.4/bacula-fd-init, -files/2.4.4/bacula-gnomesu2gksu.diff,
